https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/lyxdZFKoeIuxBKlwDoFT3RlVP17.jpg Surya Murthy lives a very wealthy lifestyle in India along with his parents, his niece, and a younger look-alike brother, Satya. His parents would like him to get married, but he refuses until Satya, who himself is anxious to get married to his girlfriend, selects a bride named Vasundhara. Events prove that Vasundhara is indeed the ideal bride for Surya, and both get married Eduruleni Manishi
